gmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af640f318f86bdaffe509a97b05ae8d82211ebc","tid":647322,"uid":124741,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T02:58:43.000Z","msg":"樓上班撚樣真係好撚柒"},{"pid":"1cf26d87a9d6ed7164c561f0ed9cdc504c5b02bc","tid":647322,"uid":17546,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T03:00:04.000Z","msg":"睇樓主將報導砍頭砍尾就知有問題啦"},{"pid":"46c8c04a9af65b7be63c311c4d6810ccc843b029","tid":647322,"uid":94402,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T03:01:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">學而自爆被踩冇價值</span><br />\n<br />\n趙學而前晚在紅館舉行演唱會，陳奕迅、蔡一傑、袁詠儀、廖碧兒、江若琳和男友蕭潤邦等捧場，張智霖（Chilam）擔任表演嘉賓。學而性感上場，她笑說：「女人可以有選擇，𠵱家啲女仔唔夠信心，加啲減啲，我堅持唔加，keep住『好平』如潮，去到老都唔會墮。」她和Chilam合唱《現代愛情故事》，<span style=\"color: orange;\">Chilam笑說：「你係少數歌手唔會話細個就聽我嘅歌大，班後輩好冇教養，以後唔再做佢哋嘉賓，𠵱家我哋都咁高咁大，老皮老肉，樂壇人瑞大戰樂壇人乾。」</span><br />\n<br />\n尾聲時，學而自揭曾遇上阻滯：「有位高權重嘅人同我講『你冇價值㗎啦』，嗰刻我冇跌落谷底，之後有另一個同我講『你唔唱歌唔使死』，所以我曾經講過要爭氣，但爭氣係好難。」騷後學而受訪時說：「你哋估啦，我唔會講係邊個。價值係自己，唔會人講一句，就抹煞自己嘅努力。」<br />\n<br />\n採訪：王連連<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180430/20376559\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180430%2F20376559&d=NuYyARMr%2BTr6a%2FgzurVG3ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=cecc9596\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180430%2F20376559&h=c49cae47\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180430/20376559</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【後輩唔識撈】張智霖鬧爆歌手冇教養 呢個人唔通係......</span><br />\n<br />\n趙學而昨晚在紅館，舉行她入行三十年第一次紅館個人騷，又歌又舞十分有睇頭，她更邀來嘉賓COOL魔張智霖。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">二人合唱完後，張智霖大爆即刻答應做她個唱嘉賓，因為自己是樂壇人瑞，趙學而是樂壇人乾，之後仲突然大爆有後輩歌手在個唱，表示自小聽他的歌長大，好無教養，他以後不會再做他的個唱嘉賓</span>。 <br />\n<br />\n翻查紀錄，過去張智霖曾做吳業坤同周柏豪演唱會嘉賓，周柏豪又講過佢睇電視劇《祝君好》，已經覺得張智霖好正。 <br />\n<br />\n唔通，呢位係......。  <br />\n<br />\n更多<span style=\"color: red;\"> 壹週刊 </span>文章　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20180430/2_584529_0/-%E5%BE%8C%E8%BC%A9%E5%94%94%E8%AD%98%E6%92%88-%E5%BC%B5%E6%99%BA%E9%9C%96%E9%AC%A7%E7%88%86%E6%AD%8C%E6%89%8B%E5%86%87%E6%95%99%E9%A4%8A-%E5%91%A2%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%94%94%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%82-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180430%2F2_584529_0%2F-%25E5%25BE%258C%25E8%25BC%25A9%25E5%2594%2594%25E8%25AD%2598%25E6%2592%2588-%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E6%2599%25BA%25E9%259C%2596%25E9%25AC%25A7%25E7%2588%2586%25E6%25AD%258C%25E6%2589%258B%25E5%2586%2587%25E6%2595%2599%25E9%25A4%258A-%25E5%2591%25A2%25E5%2580%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2594%2594%25E9%2580%259A%25E4%25BF%2582-&d=NuYyARMr%2BTr6a%2FgzurVG3ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=f62c082c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180430%2F2_584529_0%2F-%25E5%25BE%258C%25E8%25BC%25A9%25E5%2594%2594%25E8%25AD%2598%25E6%2592%2588-%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E6%2599%25BA%25E9%259C%2596%25E9%25AC%25A7%25E7%2588%2586%25E6%25AD%258C%25E6%2589%258B%25E5%2586%2587%25E6%2595%2599%25E9%25A4%258A-%25E5%2591%25A2%25E5%2580%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2594%2594%25E9%2580%259A%25E4%25BF%2582-&h=a531da2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20180430/2_584529_0/-%E5%BE%8C%E8%BC%A9%E5%94%94%E8%AD%98%E6%92%88-%E5%BC%B5%E6%99%BA%E9%9C%96%E9%AC%A7%E7%88%86%E6%AD%8C%E6%89%8B%E5%86%87%E6%95%99%E9%A4%8A-%E5%91%A2%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%94%94%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%82-</a><br />\n<br />\n垃圾寫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe92f0399552fce7ba47007348bc2dfe715b59cd","tid":647322,"uid":90166,"like":2,"d